						"copy": "<div style= \"font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1; color: rgb(255, 102, 51); margin-bottom: 20px;\" >\n  THREAT ADVISORY REPORT\n </div>\n<div style= \"font-size: 40px; font-weight: 600; line-height:1.1\" >\n  Cyber Army of Russia Reborn  \n </div><br>\n<div style= \"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; line-height:1.5\" >\n  Disruptive attack vectors\n </div><br>\n\nRecent threat data indicates a new and escalating risk posed by Cyber Army of Russia Reborn (CARR). Having already claimed responsibility for several high-profile breaches, this Russian-affiliated cyber group deploys highly effective, self-propagating malware to compromise critical infrastructure and services. This has introduced a significant threat to business operations and has provided a blueprint for attackers to successfully bypass conventional security tools.\n\nIn this report, you'll learn more about CARR, implications of these threats, and recommended actions for evaluating and mitigating exposure.\n\nIndustries targeted:\n- Public sector\n- Critical infrastructure\n- Water\n- Transportation\n- Healthcare\n- Industrial control systems\n\nLocations targeted:\n- France\n- Poland\n- United States",
